I would like some way of choosing to post to any of the spaces that I have access to.

I have found myself many times wanting to put the same news item in more than one space.  For example, a notification that I will be on vacation to show up in all of the project spaces that I work on.

The only way I know to do this is either 1) compose the same news item _x_ times or 2) use some combination of labels and the blog-post macro.  1) has the obvious downside of requiring one to repeat the same activity _x_ times.  2) is undesirable because notifications will only trigger for the space that I post to.

